Leverkusen is a very attacking team that scores a lot, but also concedes too many. In the Bundesliga, they've kept only three clean sheets after 15 rounds, whilst conceding 20 in total. This team doesn't have balance and Barca don't even have to be at their best to beat this Leverkusen team.
